  "title": "Cloud Operations Specialist (Security) - Perm Role",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong>\n<strong>Cybersecurity System Maintenance</strong>\n- Regularly monitor and maintain security tools, firewalls, antivirus software, and intrusion\ndetection/prevention systems (IDS/IPS)\n<br /><strong>Incident Response Support</strong>\n- Assist in identifying, investigating, and responding to security incidents, providing firstlevel troubleshooting and documentation\n-  Liaise with technology vendors for escalation where required\n<br /><strong>Vulnerability Management</strong>\n- Conduct regular vulnerability assessments and patch management to ensure systems\nremain secure\n<br /><strong>Security Audits</strong>\n- Support security audits by gathering and preparing necessary logs and reports. Ensure\ncompliance with security best practices and regulatory standards\n<br /><strong>Collaboration</strong>\n- Work closely with IT teams, network engineers, and other stakeholders to implement\nsecurity measures and support operational needs\n<br /><strong>Documentation</strong>\n- Maintain detailed documentation on security procedures, incidents, and the overall state\nof cybersecurity environment<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in IT / Computer Science / Engineering or equivalent</li><li>Professional certifications in cyber security solutions preferred</li><li>At least 5 years of experience in cyber security maintenance role or IT security operations</li><li>Experience in leading team, Able to lead a team of engineers to fulfil Day 1 and Day 2 functions</li><li> Strong analytical skills and attention to detail</li><li> Ability to work independently and manage multiple tasks simultaneously</li><li> Experience in either one of the multiple cyber security domain eg. (Endpoint protection,\nNetwork Security, IAM)</li><li>Certifications in CISSP or equivalent would be advantageous</li><li>Operational experience in Container Security and Key Management is a plus</li></ul><p><strong>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</strong></p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>abegail@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.</p>",
